{
  "texts": [
    "The availability of sufficient final users is a challenge in many applications.",
    "While it might be easy to find undergraduate volunteers at universities for research in iVR environments (e.g., Kampa et al. 2022), the contrary might occur in the case of testing an iVR-based therapy for a rare physical illness (e.g., Lai et al. 2020).",
    "The statistical value of the conclusions of both works will in all likelihood differ, in accordance with the numbers of final users.",
    "General-purpose responses are given to the previous points within the seven fields of application that are considered in this review: education, military, psychology, medicine, sports, tourism and marketing, and ergonomics.",
    "An eighth field, research, was added, which encompassed all the works focused on the design of an application, although with no specific final use."
  ]
}